# endgame-ai allowlist policy
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Only paths explicitly un-ignored below are tracked. Everything else is ignored
# by default (runtime logs, live_nodes, IDE/MCP harness, caches, local secrets).
#
# To track something new: add a !rule here, then git add -f <path>.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Ignore everything first
*

# Allow descending into directories we un-ignore below
!*/

# ─── Repo metadata ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
!.gitignore
!.gitattributes
!LICENSE
!README.md

# ─── Organism core (source of truth) ───────────────────────────────────────
!wiring.json
!actions.py
!brain.py
!desktop.py
!nodes.py
!organism.py
!workbench.py

# ─── Seed node templates (copied to live_nodes/ at runtime — not tracked) ───
!seed_nodes/
!seed_nodes/**